text: Ibrahima Kassory Fofana (born 1954) is a Guinean politician. He was the Prime Minister of Guinea from 24 May 2018 until the 2021 coup d'état on 5 September 2021.Guinée : Ibrahima Kassory Fofana, l'ancien opposant devient Premier ministre == References == Category:1954 births Category:Prime ministers of Guinea Category:Living people
